<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Steel, circuit boards, lights, misc. electronics components, wire, solder, hardware &#8211; 2024</h2>



<hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity"/>



<p>A wearable interactive sculpture and electrical device. When worn, the Reifier surmises and “transcribes” the wearer&#8217;s inner emotions into a display of twenty lights. Each light corresponds to a specific mood or desire, and more than one may be illuminated at a time. This output can then be read and transcribed by the surrounding audience to determine the wearer’s state of being. A new output is generated each time the wearer speaks or moves their jaw.</p>



<div style="height:20px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>The Reifier uses no microcontrollers or computer programming. Its circuitry is purpose built to fulfill this function.</p>



